Plotting

We decided to investigate how this statistic changes across the different local authorities of Greater Manchester.

Creating maps

It makes sense to represent some of this data on a map. In order to do this, we need a shapefile of Greater Manchester. We’ve downloaded the Local Authority Districts shape file from the Open Geography Portal.

Leaflet map

We then dediced to create a interactive map, using the same dataset above, but instead using the leaflet package.

In order to colour the polygons by the values, we had to first create our own palette function. We then used that palette function in the fillColor argument.
